posts.description: Having a blast in VIETNAM!🥒-When you meet people who have so little but so much happiness in their eyes all you wanna do is laugh together with them & share some of that happiness!!🙈 This lady, Mrs. Suu, was the coolest! We took a few shots and sent them to the lady who came to this local market with us; she then printed them out and gave it to the lady at the market. She said that Mrs. Suu never saw a picture of herself and was so happy and now has it with her all the time; between all the amazingly delicious smelling greens & hectic market life. Happy Tuesday everyone, smile if you haven’t yet today!🙉 xx, N 📷-@tanjasimonewuethrich #vietnam #happiness #cookbook2 #eatbetternotlesstravels

VIETNAM!🥒🥑🍏 -Officially THE heaven of herbs, leaves and most amazing food! Gosh I can’t remember the last time I loved the food in a country to a point where I almost faint because it’s so good!🐒 From all kinds of Phos, to fresh Summer Rolls, Rice Noodle dishes, Banh Cuon and all the other Banh’s and whatever everything is called- if I keep eating like this I will have Vietnamese blood running through my veins by like, tomorrow. (I hope my over-excitement made it clear enough that I simply wanted to say that the food here is THE BOMB haha!🙈) Happy new Weeek everyone, xx N #vietnam #hoian #bestfoodever #eatbetternotlesstravels #cookbook2

HELLO VIETNAM!✈️ -from 15 degrees in South-Korea to 35 degrees in Vietnam. Traveling light? Never heard of it sorry haha!🙈 Love my new bag from @loandsons, it’s so big and handy- I’m the one who always wants to take tons of stuff on the plane from laptop to camera and food. Like I usually bring a fruit-shop on the plane haha!🙊 Always bring food on your flight guys- it’s the best to pack out a juicy mango and eat it like no one’s watching while the others get airplane food. If you haven't yet- try it!🐒 Hope you all had a great Weekend, xx N #vietnam #cookbook2 #eatbetternotlesstravels #loandsons #nikonswitzerland

Kimchi-Dumplings in SEOUL, freshly steamed!🇰🇷 -holy yummm, I hope you guys can smell how delicious they taste through the picture! (P.S. -if you like garlic- visit South-Korea cause here there's garlic, and a ton of garlic, in like everything! And I absolutely LOVE IT haha!🙈) xx, N #cookbook2 #eatbetternotlesstravels #seoul #southkorea #dumplings #kimchi #vegetables

Bukchon Hanok Village, SEOUL. 🇰🇷-there's nothing I love more than exploring new countries and tasting my way through all the streets!🙈 In love with the Bibimbap (sort of like a Buddha Bowl) here- so so fresh and delicious! And yap- I'm the one who always wants a big extra portion of veggies on top. Like XXL-extra haha!🙉 Happy Weekend fellas, xx N 📷- @tanjasimonewuethrich #cookbook2 #eatbetternotlesstravels #seoul #southkorea #bukchon

Cacao-Hazelnut-Quinoa Porridge w/ homemade salted & roasted Hazelnut-Vanillabutter, fresh Bluberries, Banana & a drizzle of homemade Hazelnut-Milk.🍇 -can you tell I love Hazelnut haha?🙈 Happy Friday everyone, xx N
SEOUL, South-Korea!🇰🇷 -the haunt for Kimchi, Bibimbap, Mandu and Gimbap has started!🙈 Happy Monday, xx N 📷- @tanjasimonewuethrich #cookbook2 #eatbetternotlesstravels #seoul #southkorea #kimchiland

My kind of Easter Eggs this year!🐰🍃 HAPPY EASTER from South-East Asia everyone- enjoy it to the fullest and please eat some chocolate for me as well!🙉 I gotta get back to rice-dishes, spicy peanut-dips & fresh spring rolls! Xx, N #cookbook2 #eatbetternotlesstravels #southeastasia #eggplants
Peanut-Oats w/ Blackberry-Blueberry Coulis, fresh Figs & Blueberries and salted Hazelnut Crunch!🍇 -one of my all-time favs mhhhh!🙈 Happy Hump Day everyone, xx N

Yakeyama, Japan. Rice fields- 7th of April 2017.❄️ -just a 2 hour train ride from Tokyo and we landed in the snow. And yap- the rice fields, still covered in snow, will be ready to harvest in a few months. The farmers gave us some of their rice to try and I've never ever tasted such delicious rice!! HALLELUJA haha!🙈More pics to follow from Japan, xx N #japan #cookbook2 #eatbetternotlesstravels #itoigawa
